Looking for a T206 Jimmy Collins with Sovereign 350 back.

Art M.
[url]rebelsart@aol.com[/url]

8 years ago, when I started my all-SOVEREIGN set, I was told Jimmy Collins with a SOVEREIGN 350 back exists.

I have searched for this card since then; and, have never found one Therefore, there is a high probability that
it is a No-Print.

Whoever claimed it did exist, probably had it confused with Eddie Collins.


[url]tedzan11@comcast.net[/url]


TED Z
.

Hi Ted,
Thanks for the information.  I have that card listed on my possible list but do not remember seeing one.  It is most likely a no-print.
Art
